snippet.title: ആടുജീവിതം സിനിമയുടെ പൈറസി പ്രശ്നം: Shocking Police Case || ALICE CHRISTY
snippet.description:
The piracy issue surrounding the movie "Aadujeevitham" has led to a police case being filed. Alice Christy discusses this controversial topic in this video.

"Aadujeevitham" is a highly anticipated Malayalam film directed by Blessy, based on the novel of the same name by Benyamin. The novel tells the story of Najeeb Muhammad, an Indian immigrant who ends up trapped in the deserts of Saudi Arabia for more than two decades. The film adaptation explores themes of survival, resilience, and the human spirit in the face of extreme adversity.

Najeeb, the protagonist, migrates to the Middle East in search of better opportunities to support his family back home in Kerala, India. However, due to unforeseen circumstances, he finds himself stranded in the desert with no means of escape. The harsh environment and isolation take a toll on his physical and mental well-being.

As the years pass, Najeeb struggles to survive amidst the vast expanse of sand, battling loneliness, despair, and the elements. His only companions are the memories of his past life and his unwavering determination to stay alive against all odds.

Throughout his journey, Najeeb encounters various challenges, including hunger, thirst, and the threat of wildlife. Yet, he remains steadfast in his resolve to endure and eventually find a way back to civilization.

The story of "Aadujeevitham" is a poignant exploration of the human condition, depicting the resilience of the human spirit in the face of unimaginable hardships. It delves into themes of survival, hope, and the innate will to live, offering a powerful and moving narrative that resonates with audiences.

#AaduJeevitham #AaduJeevithamMovie #BlessyFilm #BenyaminNovel
#SurvivalMovie #DesertSurvival #MalayalamFilm #IndianCinema #Resilience #HumanSpirit

snippet.title: केजरीवाल ने कोर्ट में पेश की अपनी दलील | Kejriwal presents his case to Court
snippet.description:
अरविंद केजरीवाल को आज कोर्ट से राहत नहीं मिली, उन्हें एक अप्रैल को फिर से पेश किया जाएगा। लेकिन आज राउज़ ऐवन्यू कोर्ट में केजरीवाल ईडी पर भारी पड़ गए। अरविंद केजरीवाल ने कहा कि वे अपनी रिमांड का विरोध करने नहीं आए हैं। ईडी जब तक चाहे जेल में रख सकती है। मगर आज अपनी दलील में केजरीवाल ने दिखा दिया है कि वे जेल भेजने की राजनीति के भय से आज़ाद हो गए हैं, उन्हें पता है कि यही आज की नियति है।

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 37 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 28th March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum

Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 38 Teaser - 28th March 2024 - Har Pal Geo
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 38 Teaser - 28th March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya
Mehmood Akhtar as Zaawar  
Agha Mustafa as Rayyan  
Hamzah Tariq as Rufi
Ayesha Rajpoot as Shagufta
Mizna Waqas as Husna
Sohail Masood as Mirza Sahab
Birjees Farooqui as Salma

#Khumar
#FerozeKhan
#NeelamMuneer

snippet.title: YAARIYAN (Official Video) Billa Sonipat Ala | Deepty | Latest Haryanvi Songs 2024 | Haryanvi Gaana
snippet.description:
White Hill Dhaakad presents the official video of Billa Sonipat Ala's new release "Yaariyan". Written and composed by Billa Sonipat Ala himself and music given by Deepty, this New Haryanvi Song is dedicated to the unbreakable bonds of friendship.
Produced by Gunbir Singh Sidhu and Manmord Singh Sidhu.

|| Meri maa ke sare ladle, Na kalla Sonipat ala re ||
Like, Comment and Share with all your friends...😍


Credits :
Singer : Billa Sonipat Ala
Lyrics / Composer : Billa Sonipat Ala
Featuring: Billa Sonipat Ala, Vikram Sarkar, R Maan, Lakshay Malik
Music : Deepty
Mix & Master. : D Chandu
Directed By : Lakshay Malik
DOP : Arundeep Teji
Focus : Monu 
Ad : Seena Shekhpuria
Video : Team All Good
Project By : Ricky Rapria

Artist Coordination / Online Promotions : HOT (Hub Of Talent) https://www.instagram.com/hub_of_talent/
Produced by : Gunbir Singh Sidhu and Manmord Singh Sidhu




🗒 Lyrics : 
Yaari mahri sabpe bhari
Yaari ya dhumme thari
Jigre ka rola hai bhai 
Palat denge duniya sari
Hojyave hai jade khade 
Ude matter hojya bade bade
Laage salami yaari mein
Na position koyi sarkari
Yaari mahri sabpe bhari
Yaari ya dhumme thari
Jigre ka rola hai bhai 
Palat denge duniya sari

Tu hasse te mera din ban ja
Tere russe te ghor andhera hai
Bhagwan dikhe manne tere mein
Re dil sone ka lehrya se
Tere jaisa yaar nahi
Yo yari dekh misal bani
Koye bole galt tere bare je
Main muh pe dedu gaal ghanni
Dil ke dhani manne yaar mile
Na ek bhi dil ka kala re 
Meri maa ke sare ladle
Na kalla sonipat ala re

Dharam veer ki jodi hai ya tode te na tuttegi
Jisdin chhod ke chale jahaan re dekhiyo andhi utthegi
Mere khater ram hai tu tera hanuman sa bhakat hu main
Bas marya jiu tere karke na itna jayada sakhat hu main
Ajya mat roos ke bhaje 
Duniya mein chhod dyu aaj ae
Fikka sab tere aage 
Rishta gehra gel teri
Kad ka karu maana maana
Kyate tu mare bahna
Muh band karde aake sabka
Na duniya sali degi tanna
Us chita pe teri gel jalu 
Teri maut ne gale ke la lyunga
Meri bhola baba sunya kare
Main sirpe duniya tha lyunga

Episode 4043: April Fool Banayenge
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal plans to spend time with friends, while Jethalal and his pals discuss April Fool’s Day. They devise a playful prank to fool the entire Gokuldham society.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4043, 27 Mar 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

LYRICS

Uski tareefein mujhe jis ne banaya
Chandi jaisa rang baal sone jaisa paya
Kehnda menu sheesha hai gajab teri kaya
Saaye ko mere Haan thodi mujhse jalan hai
Choo ke mujhe jalne ka uska bhi Mann hai
Roop ki adaalat bheje daily hi summon hai
 
Main nahi Lok hi saare mere naal yahi kehna chaahe,
Doharaayein.
 
Every time I look in to the mirror I say
Thank you, God
You did a damn good job
Give him a round of applause
And all the boys go
Ah ah ah
 
Thank you, God
You did a damn good job
Does the queen need a Raj?
And everybody goes
Ah ah ah
 
 
Hadbadi na koi mujhko banane mein ki
Bana ke khud nu kaha oh teri
Na honi hun toh kabhi koi aisi
 
Nikon
She’s flash camera lights on
She the Snake charmer
Gon catch the python
Hitz only
Call her Mike Tyson
Breakin’ boys necks
From Jay Sean to Jason
 
Aye aye
Money money
Aye aye aye
Dhvani Dhvani
Aye aye aye
Ya Twenty twenty late
 
Well Thank God
That she’s what God made
 
Main nahi Lok hi saare mere naal yahi kehna chaahe,
Doharaayein.
 
Every time I look in to the mirror I say
Thank you, God
You did a damn good job
Give him a round of applause
And all the boys go
Ah ah ah
 
Thank you, God
you did a damn good job
does the queen need a Raj?
And everybody goes
Ah ah ah
 
Thank you, God

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Watch all the exciting clips of Holi Special: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1esHln9KXStCbSKq6ifX0a

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

Written By: Saqlain Abbas
Directed By: Syed Wajahat Hussain
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

snippet.title: Ford പുതിയ Endeavour ഇന്ത്യയിലേക്ക് തിരിച്ചെത്തിക്കുന്നു.തായ്‌ലൻഡിലുള്ള ആ മോഡലിന്റെ ടെസ്റ്റ് ഡ്രൈവ്
snippet.description:
എൻഡേവർ എന്ന എസ് യുവിയും റേഞ്ചർ എന്ന പിക്കപ്പ് ട്രക്കുമായാണ് ഫോർഡ് ഈ വര്ഷം ഇന്ത്യയിലേക്ക് തിരിച്ചു വരുന്നത്.ഇവ രണ്ടും തുടക്കത്തിൽ തായ്‌ലൻഡിൽ നിന്ന് ഇറക്കുമതി ചെയ്യുകയാണ്.തായ്‌ലൻഡിൽ നിലവിലുമ്മ മോഡലുകളാണ് ഇന്ത്യയിലേക്ക് വരിക എന്നർഥം.തായ്‌ലൻഡിൽ പോയി ആ രണ്ടു മോഡലുകളും ഓടിച്ച കഥ കേൾക്കുക,കാണുക..

For more information on programs, admission requirements, fees structure, post study work rights, etc get in touch with Fair Future.

Also students can apply through Fair Future to study in Canada, Australia, France, UK, New Zealand, Spain, etc. 

Fair Futures 50th batch to study in Canada from Kerala is also the September 2024 batch. To apply for programs in Canada as well through one of Kerala’s oldest overseas education consultants for Canada get in touch with them.

Get in touch with Fair Future now :

Cochin Office : Fair Future Overseas Educational Consultancy Pvt Ltd Fair Future Edifice, East of Ravipuram Junction off M.G.Road, Near Ravipuram Sree Krishna Swami Temple, Cochin 682016 Ph : 1800 419 1210, 0484 2356699 | info@fairfutureonline.com Office Hours : 10 AM to 6 PM, Monday to Saturday.
